(33, 2, 23, 'scada', 'Kontrolmatik - Bereket Enerji Göktaş-1 HEPP DCS Project', 'Kontrolmatik - Bereket Enerji Göktaş-1 HEPP DCS Project', 'As Kontrolmatik and Bereket Enerji, we have made the whole Göktaş-1 HEPP system monitorable and controllable ', 'As Kontrolmatik and Bereket Enerji, we have made the whole Göktaş-1 HEPP system monitorable and controllable through automation. By means of integrated monitoring and control, the faults occurring in the system can be identified and fastly solved. Thus, assistance in increasing the production, continuity and efficiency of the plant is provided.\nGoktas-1 HEPP project, which is a 2-unit 120 MW power plant, has been commissioned in cooperation with Bereket Energy.\n\nThe purpose is,\n\nMinimizing human-induced errors in production. Ensuring systematic operation of the plant. Determining the source of the failure occurred in order to sort it out as soon as possible, Establishing the synchronous system for production. Result,\n\nIt became a plant that can be controlled and monitored from a single point. Systematic controls have been added to prevent operator malfunctioning. For the safety of the plant, Start Stop operations are controlled by a single command through DCS. The faults that occur in the power plant are shown on the scada screen in order of time and their logs are kept. This way, occurring failures can directly be responded. Installed Synchronous system 2 turbines can be synchronized to 2 different busbars with one system. When the power is cut off in the AG distribution system, the automatic diesel generator takes over and feeds the Urgent loads that are in need of internal power. This way, failure that might occur due to black outs can be prevented. With the ABB 800xA DCS system installed, the Dam Gates which are 14 km away from the power plant can be controlled. Advantages of Kontrolmatik,\nTo provide reliable business opportunities in the changing and developing energy sector, to produce solutions that can minimize human-induced errors and to adapt the solutions it produces to its personnel and corporate culture.\n\nBereket Enerji,\n\nBereket enerji produces electricity utilizing geothermal, hydroelectric, thermal, solar, wind and landfill gas resources. Bereket Enerji handles design, construction, installation and management of the power plants it built.\nContact Kontrolmatik for more!\n', NULL, 'kontrolmatik-bereket-enerji-goktas-1-hepp-dcs-project', 'Kontrolmatik - Bereket Enerji Göktaş-1 HEPP DCS Project', 'DRAFT', '0', '2019-09-13 05:04:24', '2020-01-31 06:53:44', 'Kontrolmatik - Bereket Enerji Göktaş-1 HEPP DCS Project', '[]', NULL, 'en', ''),
(34, 2, 26, 'training', 'Kontrolmatik - Training on Effective Speaking on Phone', 'Kontrolmatik - Training on Effective Speaking on Phone', 'In the weekend training with subject \"Effective Speaking on Phone\", which we carried out in Dialog iletisim on 07.10.2017 / 08.10.2017, which is meant to support self-improvement of our employees and which is not taught to us during school years and in business life; both the institution providing the training and the instructor were excellent.', 'In the weekend training with subject \"Effective Speaking on Phone\", which we carried out in Dialog iletisim on 07.10.2017 / 08.10.2017, which is meant to support self-improvement of our employees and which is not taught to us during school years and in business life; both the institution providing the training and the instructor were excellent.\n\n\nAt the end of the training, we have seen once again that each individual should receive this education which adds considerable value to our personal development.\n\nWe were quite satisfied with the institution and training. We hope we will be able to participate in trainings with various subjects and that our Company can provide such opportunities for our employees in order to add value to them. We would like to thank Senior Management of our company and our trainer Metin Yavuzoğlu.\n\n\n\n', 'blog_posts/January2020/jTbHEqwVNylYsj5HR5oQ.jpg', 'kontrolmatik-training-on-effective-speaking-on-phone', 'Kontrolmatik - Training on Effective Speaking on Phone', 'DRAFT', '0', '2019-09-13 05:09:19', '2020-01-30 06:32:21', 'Kontrolmatik - Training on Effective Speaking on Phone', '[\"Training\"]', NULL, 'en', ''),
(35, 2, 26, 'training', 'Kontrolmatik - Project Management Training', 'Kontrolmatik - Project Management Training', 'We participated in the PMP (Project Management Professional) certificate program for 5 days in order to increase the project management competencies of the executives and manager ', 'We participated in the PMP (Project Management Professional) certificate program for 5 days in order to increase the project management competencies of the executives and manager candidates within the company and to raise awareness on project management methodology subjects. We have emphasized the following competencies which were expected to raise awareness in the training given by PMI (Project Management Institute);\n\n* Verbal and Written Communication Skills\n*	Meeting Management\n*	Unauthorized Impact\n*	Presentation and Public Speaking Skills\n*	Negotiation Techniques\n*	Effective Team Management\n*	Creative Thinking Techniques\n*	Motivation and Feedback\n*	Conflict Management\n*	Decision Making\n*	Time Management and Prioritization\nWe would like to thank all our colleagues and Istanbul Institute employees for their participation.\n\nHope to meet you in new trainings…\n\n\n', NULL, 'kontrolmatik-project-management-training', 'Kontrolmatik - Project Management Training', 'DRAFT', '0', '2019-09-13 05:12:17', '2020-01-30 06:48:54', 'Kontrolmatik - Project Management Training', '[\"Training\"]', NULL, 'en', ''),
(36, 2, 26, 'training', 'Kontrolmatik - Effective Speaking and Presentation Skills Training', 'Kontrolmatik - Effective Speaking and Presentation Skills Training', 'As Kontrolmatik, we continue to learn every day in order to provide more efficient and quality service to our customers in line with our developing business and communication', 'As Kontrolmatik, we continue to learn every day in order to provide more efficient and quality service to our customers in line with our developing business and communication objectives. We emphasize the importance of communication between people once again with the support of career development we provide to our colleagues.\n\nOn 16-17 September 2017, we organized \"Effective Speaking and Presentation Skills Training\" with the contributions of Dialog İletişim and pleasant narration of Mr. Ayhan KAVAS. Through this training, we have developed our awareness of using body and language effectively, comfortably and confidently during speaking, presentation or communication. We emphasized the correct use of communication, which is one of the most important elements in our business and daily life, to produce effective and fast solutions.\n\nWe would like to thank all our colleagues, Mr. Ayhan KAVAS and Dialog İletişim employees who participated in the training.\n\nHope to meet you in new trainings…\n', NULL, 'kontrolmatik-effective-speaking-and-presentation-skills-training', 'Kontrolmatik - Effective Speaking and Presentation Skills Training', 'DRAFT', '0', '2019-09-13 05:19:50', '2020-01-30 06:43:58', 'Kontrolmatik - Effective Speaking and Presentation Skills Training', '[\"Training\"]', NULL, 'en', '');
