(2, 1, 'About Us l Kontrolmatik', 'About Us', 'Kontrolmatik’s main activity is providing **Operational Technology Solutions** for infrastructure projects in **Power Plants, Electricity Transmission and Distribution Facilities, Oil, Gas, Sugar, Fertilizer, Paper, Cement, Mine etc Industrial Processes** and **Transportation** sector. \r\n\r\nKontrolmatik Services are providing all necessary basic and detail engineering, procurement, construction, testing and commissioning under a single roof from turn-to-end for operational technology packages such as protection, control, monitoring, software, communication, instrumentation, balance of plants, all electrical, electromechanical, mechanical, construction and construction works of the above facilities and sectors. \r\n\r\nAdditionally, Kontrolmatik realizes Information Technologies Integration projects for control systems, with its services as end to end cyber security packages, digitalization, data analytics and algorithyms.\r\n\r\n**1-Operational Technologies and Industrial Software & Control Systems** Simply put, OT (Operational Technologies) is a physical infrastructure (temperature, established for a power plant, an industrial facility, a mine site or a transportation line (rail system or road). Process instruments for monitoring various process values such as pressure, flow, control valves, motors, conveyors and other machines to control these values and prevent dangerous conditions, communication infrastructure (Ethernet switches, serial converters, fiber) required to carry this physical infrastructure to the computer environment optical switches, routers, etc.) and control systems that enable automatic control and monitoring of these systems (Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition System (SCADA), Distributed Control System (DCS), Programmable Logic Controller (PLC), Manufacturing Execution System (MES), Product Lifecycle Management (PLM), Ent erprise Resource Planning (ERP), Human Machine Interface (HMI) etc. ) and IT Infrastructure (Server, PC, Monitor, Printer, HardDrive etc.).\r\n\r\n**2-Communication, Information Security and Internet of Things - IOT**Industrial Communication, Ethernet Switches, Media Converters (Fiber-Copper), Routers, SDHs, Multiplexers, Modems, Firewalls and Gateways, control these products Network analysis and management software, network security software and integration, engineering and installation services of all these systems, Information Security and Internet of Things (IOT), IOT based sensors and field equipment, IOT Platforms and Software, Data It consists of Analytical Software, Deep Learning, Machine Learning Algorithm and softwares, End-to-end cyber security analysis, passive listening, active intervention, all integration with all software and equipment, PKI services, MDS (Managed Detection Services) Services, Penetration Tests, and training and consultancy services.\r\n\r\n**3-Power Systems and Project Management** Today\'s electrical networks are characterized by their size and complexity as well as new technologies and techniques for power generation, transmission, distribution, protection and measurement. These power systems can operate at high, medium or low voltage levels. Power systems, turbines required for electricity production, all switchgear equipment and transformers required for transmission and distribution, starting from generators, and a huge collection of products and services with all technology infrastructures and control systems required for the protection and control of systems.\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20About.png)', NULL, 'about-us', 'About Us', 'About Us', 'ACTIVE', '2019-07-24 08:01:03', '2020-04-29 11:07:31', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(3, 2, 'Overview l Kontrolmatik', 'Overview', 'Kontrolmatik provides comprehensive services in various markets such as energy, transportation, mining, process and public service, to decommission from the concept, to support its customers in the entire life cycle of their customers\' assets.\r\n\r\nThe foundations of Kontrolmatik were laid when three young entrepreneurs came together to realize their ideals in **2007** .  \r\n\r\nThe first work that Kontrolmatik, which was established in January **2008** was converted into invoice is Microsoft Head Office Building - Building Automation and Weak Current System project. Kontrolmatik,with this project and with the experience gained from the company they work before for Automation and many projects in Turkey , they completed Azerbaijan Zagalata Airport Airport Building Automation Works, which is the first foreign business, has been signed in January 2008 again with the trust and relationships it provides in these areas. After this work, they continued work in abroad in Libya, Sirte Airport, in Azerbaijan Haydar Aliyev Presidential Palace, building automation and electrification works.\r\n\r\nIn **2010** Kontrolmatik signed business partnerships on a global basis with the industry\'s leading electrical company ABB Electric Company.\r\n\r\nThe most important projects that keep a priority in Kontrolmatik\'s growth strategy in the transport sector as firstly Levent Hisarüstü metro project that Kontrolmatik perform in  **2011**.  It followed by the longest subway line, which is Kartal -Kadıköy Metro with Eurasia Metro Group for  ECS and Automation Systems and İkitelli-Olympiyat Metro Line with Gülermak-Doğuş for  ECS and Automation Systems works . Along with these works, it took part in the prestigious metro projects in both Asian and European sides of Istanbul and increased his efficiency in the transportation sector, Üsküdar-Ümraniye Metro Line with Doğuş Construction for  ECS, Tunnel Ventilation and Control Room, Mahmutbey-Mecidiyeköy Metro Line with Alarko for LV Panel Systems),. Additinally they worked for TCDD Turkish Railway Authority Telekomand Centers (Çerkezköy, Adana, İzmir, Malatya, Sivas, Ankara) and Tunnel Electromechanical Systems (Istanbul Taksim, Ankara Protocol) projects \r\n\r\nAs of **2011** , Kontrolmatik has decided to increase its fields of activity and started to work in the Energy sector in addition to the Building Technologies and Transportation Systems sectors. They started by establishing Control Systems in 4 Gas Power Plants of Zorlu Energy, and then completed his first works abroad in this sector with the works of the Power Plant and High Voltage Switchgear Center in the Sulaimaniye and Erbil regions of Iraq.\r\n\r\nIn **2012**  Kontrolmatik increase the activity in Power Plants and High Voltage Switchgear Centers projects abroad, especially in Turkey and Iraq, Turkmenistan, Saudi Arabia, Afghanistan, has completed projects in countries such as Jordan.\r\n\r\nIn **2012**,  Kontrolmatik signed its first project in Africa for the Tanas Beles Sugar factory  in Ethiopia. Later, later they also worked in Omo Kuraz Sugar Factory project, which is a continuation of tprevious one in the same country, and also supported and pioneered the establishment of a local panel manufacturing factory of the state institution\r\n\r\nIn **2013**, Kontrolmatik, which increased its activities in the Energy and Transportation sector, took part in various projects such as tunnel electromechanical projects in Ankara and Istanbul, and the Power Plant in Zonguldak and Siirt and completed the scopes.\r\n\r\nIn **2014** Eti Kırka Compressor Station, which is the first Turnkey project Kontrolmatik has received its tender from Eti Maden. This project is the first work that Kontrolmatik has completed in all its scope as construction-mechanical-electrical and automation.\r\n\r\nIn **2014** Completed its first business in Europe in 2014 ** with Limak Pristina Airport Energy Monitoring System.\r\n\r\n**2015** - Turkey\'s largest Organized Industrial Zone, which has completed its Ikitelli OSB Energy Management System project. This was one of the largest distribution network in Turkey and the project was one of the biggest Energy Management System project.\r\n\r\nIn **2016** , 3x175 MW and 2x175 MW,2 Power Plant projects in Africa undertook all EBOP electrical coverage and 220kV High Voltage Switchgear Center and signed the highest consistent contract until that date.\r\n\r\nIn **2016** ,  Kontrolmatik,  followed the trends of the sectors, opened its Software and IoT department and started to invest in the current trend in Industry 4.0 and Industry in Technology and Cyber ​​Security.\r\n\r\nUpdating the corporate organizational structure in order to respond to increasing EPC works as of **2017**  Kontrolmatik divided the technical activities in the company into 6 departments as Turnkey Projects, Engineering, Testing and Commissioning, Control Systems, Communication Systems, Software and IoT and strengthened its systematic approach. .\r\n\r\n**2018** In Software and IoT area, For one of the country\'s most prestigious projects  Istanbul Grand Airport project  Kontrolmatik served for IOT-Lorawan,  Counter Monitoring System project through until conducted one of the largest IOT project in Turkey.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn October **2018**,Kontrolmatik signed  the contract for 4 132kV GIS & AIS substations to be located in Mosul as part of the reconstruction of Iraq with MOE Ministry of Electricity.. German development bank KfW has undertaken the project financing by consulting and controlling services Fichtner. All the engineering, design, production, construction, installation and commissioning services for turn-key control systems, 132/33/11 kV substations, have been undertaken on turnkey basis. The project has been the largest EPC contract signed by a Turkish firm with MoE as the Substation EPC works in Iraq in recent years.\r\n\r\n**2019**- Kontrolmatik signed partnership agreements with General Electric In Control Systems,  , with Nozomi in the cyber security field Networks and with Fortinet,  with PSI-Germany in Production Management System, with OSISoft in Data Management Systems in local and global base.\r\n\r\nAs of  **2019** , Kontrolmatik with more than 200 staff consisting of 60% engineers, 4 Technical, 5 Administrative divisions, 4 offices in Dubai, Dortmund, Iraq and Istanbul, and 1 panel factory in Istanbul. With more than 300 projects completed in 24 different countries, it continues at full speed.\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20Presence.png)', NULL, 'overview', 'Overview', 'Overview', 'INACTIVE', '2019-07-26 06:40:53', '2020-05-11 05:56:28', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(4, 3, 'Safety l Kontrolmatik', 'Safety', 'Safety is more than a policy manual or a training video; it’s how we do business and it’s how we live 24/7. Kontrolmatik invites you to experience our culture of caring – a culture in which safety, health and welfare are top priorities; and in which we’re all responsible for looking out for one another.\r\n\r\nKontrolmatik\'s safety culture extends outside the office walls, beyond the project site and into our cars, our homes, and our communities; affecting all the people we interact with everywhere around the world. It’s about every one of us making safety a personal value that we live by each day.\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20Safety%202%20Resize%2060.jpg)', NULL, 'safety', 'Safety', 'Safety', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 08:54:37', '2020-04-29 11:10:40', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(5, 4, 'Our Advantage l Kontrolmatik', 'Our Advantage', 'Innovation is a driving force in our business, the need to improve spans people, processes and technology and we are always looking for better ways to deliver for the benefit of our customers and our business.\r\n\r\nAt Kontrolmatik we bring new thinking and fresh ideas to every project. Our drive to continuously improve runs throughout our organisation.\r\n\r\nA key part of our culture, innovation applies to our people, processes and technologies; pushing us to perform better and constantly look for opportunities to move our business forward.\r\n\r\nOur ever growing range of services brings new and exciting connections to technologies and methods that lead the way across our business. We draw from wider industry best practice in dozens of markets across hundreds of locations to offer fresh approaches and new solutions.\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20Advantages%20Resize%2060.jpg)', NULL, 'our-advantage', 'Our Advantage', 'Our Advantage', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 08:58:58', '2020-04-29 11:11:04', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(6, 5, 'Locations l Kontrolmatik', 'Locations', 'Locations\r\n\r\n**Kontrolmatik Main Office**- Tekstilkent Koza Plaza A BLok Kat 15. Esenler/İstanbul\r\n\r\n**Kontrolmatik Kuwait** - P.O.Box 9678 – Ahmadi 61007   |   Kuwait\r\n\r\n**Kontrolmatik Iraq**  (Agent) -  Irakq /Musul/almohandisen - Iraq/Duhok/KRO', NULL, 'locations', 'Locations', 'Locations', 'ACTIVE', '2019-08-06 09:06:44', '2020-08-12 05:40:20', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(7, 6, 'Partnerships l Kontrolmatik', 'Partnerships', 'By establishing long-term partnerships with the global players of the industry, Kontrolmatik increases its quality and skills, makes its business sustainable and strengthens its corporate structure. \r\n\r\n**GE - General Electric** is one of the largest companies in the industry that provides technology solutions to the public and private sectors in the healthcare, energy generation, aviation, lighting and transportation sectors. It is the solution partner in the fields of Air Insulated High Voltage Equipment and Protection Control and Monitoring Products required for Control, Substations and Electricity Production and Distribution Facilities. Air Isolated in the field of High Voltage Equipment Turkey is the only partner and reseller in Turkey and Afghanistan through private treaty market (dealers) serves as.\r\n\r\n**Baker Hughes** -  Baker Hughes is one of the largest Energy Technology companies in the region. Kontrolmatik is the first partner of Baker Hughes in Turkey and they started partnership for Nexus Control Systems in Turkey  in 2019.\r\n\r\n**ABB**- is a technology leader that guides digital transformation in industries with its history of more than 130 years. Kontrolmatik is making partnership with ABB for more than 10 years ; as with groups SASPG and Generator Excitation Systems division on a global scale ,  with the Drive section on Turkey.\r\n\r\n**Fortinet**- A multinational American company based in Sunnyvale, California. It develops and markets cyber security software and devices and services such as firewalls, antivirus, intrusion prevention, and endpoint security. Kontrolmatik and Fortinet Turkey has partnered with cyber security contract for office equipment and software.\r\n\r\n**Osisoft** - OSIsoft, LLC is an application software manufacturer for real-time data management called PI System. Founded in 1980, OSIsoft is specially located in San Leandro, California. Its partnership with Kontrolmatik à Osisoft started in 2017.\r\n\r\n**Nozomi**- Nozomi Networks, OT and IoT working in safety and visibility. The company is a pioneer and leader in its field, combining cyber security visibility for critical infrastructure, energy, manufacturing, mining, transportation, building automation and other OT sites, headquarters in San Francisco, United States. Kontrolmatik\'s partnership with Nozomi Networks started in 2017 and Kontrolmatik is the first  partner  of Nozomi in Turkey.\r\n\r\n**Cisco** - Cisco Systems is an American multinational network technologies company with headquarters in San Jose, California. Kontrolmatik started its partnership with Cisco IOT products and systems in 2017.\r\n\r\n**Commvault**- Commvault software is an enterprise-level data platform that contains modules to back up, restore, archive, replicate, and search data. It is built from the ground-up on a single platform and unified code base. Kontrolmatik became Commvault Partner in Turkey at 2019.\r\n\r\n**IXSEP**- 	IONEX Separations was founded to deliver low cost and efficient separation technology to the process industries using the IXSEP-RDA system, a revolutionary 3rd generation continuous counter current adsorption separation device.  Kontrolmatik starting agreements for Turkey market was signed first in 2015.\r\n\r\n**Espindesa (Technicas Reuinadas)** - ESPINDESA one hundred percent TECNICAS REUNIDAS, S.A. partnership for Turkey market began in 2020 with Kontrolmatik\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/August2019/YJprQyleiMNDVL2Zo0j0.png)', NULL, 'partnerships', 'Partnerships', 'Partnerships', 'ACTIVE', '2019-08-06 09:19:53', '2021-10-14 04:29:47', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(8, 7, 'Join Us l Kontrolmatik', 'Join Us', 'Kontrolmatik creates a working environment where our employees enjoy working every day and our customers want to work with us. Our success depends on feeling part of a team that we can trust the people around us. Our culture supports us to perform better and seek opportunities to move our business forward.\r\n\r\nEverything we do is built on our commitment to do the right thing for our customers, employees and communities.\r\n\r\nWhile determining our values, we pay attention to being human-oriented, taking care of nature and the environment, and to the satisfaction and happiness of our customers. \r\n\r\n• To catch all the new technologies in its field and to dominate the current\r\n• To be beneficial to the place and environment where you live.\r\n• To be side by side with all employees and to be sympathetic\r\n• To be honest, to keep what you promise.\r\n• To be compatible and to oversee all stakeholders\r\n• Approaching all projects based on technique and science\r\n• Protecting nature and its employees\r\n• Doing the job you know best, in the best way\r\n\r\nMaintaining the satisfaction of its customers and employees is our most important value in order to guarantee not only today but also the future of our company. The most important principle we observe in ensuring this is to minimize any damage to our employees, third parties, property and environment.\r\n\r\nTherefore;\r\n\r\n• To be responsible for Health, Safety, Environment and Quality with all managers and employees, to comply with the relevant laws, regulations and regulations.\r\n• To comply with the standard and customer specifications, minimize customer complaints, repetition and repair rate, reduce costs and reflect to customers.\r\n• To increase the efficiency of Management Systems, to continuously monitor and improve applications\r\n\r\nIt is the main principles of our company.\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20Site%20Resized%2060.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\nShare your CV with us to be a part of our team and to add value to our values and take part in state-of-the-art projects in different geographies and industries.\r\n\r\n**hr@kontrolmatik.com**', NULL, 'join-us', 'Join Us', 'Join Us', 'ACTIVE', '2019-08-06 10:18:00', '2020-04-29 11:13:18', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(9, 8, 'Quality And Environment l Kontrolmatik', 'Quality And Environment', '**Quality Policy**\n\nKontrolmatik **commits;**\n\nDocumenting, certifying and continuously improving our quality management system to meet the requirements of **ISO 9001: 2015** standard,\nBased on the Total Quality philosophy, achieving the company and unit targets within the team spirit,\nReviewing business processes through self-evaluation process, identifying preventive approaches to improve performance,\nIncreasing the efficiency of all processes to internationally competitive level in line with the continuous improvement approach,\nEncouraging innovative and creative approaches, managing the activities to increase technical and behavioral competencies in an integrated way with Environmental, Occupational Health and Safety Management Systems.\n\n**Environment Policy**\n\nKontrolmatik **commits;**\n\n* To protect our environment and to ensure continuity, by observing all environmental laws and regulations to control the environmental impacts and reducing the impact of our environmental performance by continuously improving and realizing this awareness, to leave a clean environmentable environment for future generations.\n* To provide continuous improvement and improvement by providing all legal requirements and environmental requirements.\n* To consider environmental impacts in production investments.\n* Minimizing all our wastes, preventing pollution at the source, reclaiming as much as possible, eliminating the non-recyclable wastes in a way that will not harm the environment, thus reducing the effects on the environment.\n* To educate our employees, suppliers and subcontractors about the environment by raising environmental awareness.\n* To continuously improve our environmental management system in order to increase our environmental performance.\n* To undertake periodic reviews to achieve these goals and objectives.', NULL, 'quality-and-environment', 'Quality And Environment', 'Quality And Environment', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 10:21:50', '2020-02-23 09:42:49', 'en', '', NULL),
(10, 1, 'A propos de nous l Kontrolmatik', 'A propos de nous', 'Kontrolmatik fournit des services de projets complets:\r\nEPCM ( Ingénierie, Approvisionnement, Supervision de construction et gestion de projet), aussi bien que les projets TURNKEY.\r\nQue ce soit la conception et la construction d’une nouvelle usine, modification ou extension, nous ajustons nos services pour répondre aux éxigences spécifiques des marchés mondiaux.', 'pages/January2021/vbKC7NI8P41mNEsz5ukZ.png', 'a-propos-de-nous', 'A propos de nous', 'A propos de nous', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-29 10:42:18', '2021-01-26 14:55:35', 'fr', NULL, NULL),
(11, 1, 'معلومات عنا', 'معلومات عنا', 'في ما يخصنا\r\n في تقديم ** حلول تكنولوجية تشغيلية لمشاريع البنية التحتية في ** Kontrolmatik يتمثل النشاط الرئيسي لشركة \r\n \r\nمحطات توليد الكهرباء ، ومنشآت نقل وتوزيع الكهرباء ، والنفط ، والغاز ، والسكر ، الأسمدة والورق والاسمنت والمناجم ، إلخ………… العمليات الصناعية ** و ** قطاع النقل. **\r\n\r\nجميع وظائف الهندسة الأساسية وتجارة التجزئة والمشتريات والبناء والاختبار والتشغيل تحت سقف  توفر خدماتKontrolmatik\r\n\r\nواحد شامل لحزم التكنولوجيا التشغيلية مثل الحماية ، التحكم ، والمراقبة ، والبرمجيات ، والاتصالات ، والأجهزة ، وموازنة المصنع ، وجميع الأعمال الكهربائية ، والكهروميكانيكية ، والميكانيكية ، والبناء والتشييد للمنشآت والقطاعات المذكورة أعلاه.\r\n بالاضافة الى ذلك بتنفيذ مشاريع تكامل تكنولوجيا المعلومات لأنظمة التحكم ، مع خدماتها في شكل حزم الأمن Kontrolmatik تقوم \r\nالسيبراني الشامل والمسح الضوئي وتحليل البيانات الخوارزميات.\r\n\r\n1- التقنيات التشغيلية والبرامج الصناعية وأنظمة التحكم ** بعبارة أخرى ، (التقنيات التشغيلية) هي بنية تحتية مادية (درجة الحرارة ، تم إنشاؤها لمحطة طاقة أو منشأة صناعية أو موقع تعدين أو خط نقل (نظام أدوات السكك الحديدية أو العمليات لمراقبة قيم العمليات المختلفة مثل الضغط والتدفق وصمامات التحكم والمحركات والناقلات والآلات الأخرى للتحكم في هذه القيم ومنع الظروف الخطرة والبنية التحتية للاتصالات (محولات إيثرنت ، والمحولات التسلسلية ، والألياف) اللازمة لنقل هذه البنية التحتية المادية إلى بيئة تكنولوجيا المعلومات (المفاتيح الضوئية ، وأجهزة التوجيه ، وما إلى ذلك).\r\n), ونظام التحكم الموزعSCADA وأنظمة التحكم التي تسمح بالتحكم الآلي والمراقبة لهذه الأنظمة (نظام التحكم والحصول على البيانات (\r\n, وتخطيط موارد (PLM) إدارة دورة حياة المنتج  (MES) , ونظام تنفيذ التصنيع (PLC) ، والتحكم المنطقي القابل للبرمجة (DCS)\r\n, و ما الى ذلك,  والبنية التحتية لتكنولوجيا المعلومات (الخادم ، جهاز الكمبيوتر, (HMI) , واجهة الإنسان للآلة  (ERP) المؤسسات\r\n، شاشة ، طابعة ، محرك أقراص ثابتة ، إلخ).\r\nومحولات الوسائطEthernet, الاتصالات الصناعية ومفاتيح  IOT\r\n\r\nالاتصالات وأمن المعلومات وإنترنت الأشياء  -2\r\nوأجهزة الإرسال المتعددة وأجهزة المودم والجدران النارية  والبوابات والتحكم في هذه المنتجات SDH(الألياف النحاسية) والموجهات و\r\nبرامج تحليل وإدارة الشبكة ، وبرامج أمان الشبكات والتكامل ، وخدمات الهندسة والتركيب لجميع هذه الأنظمة ، وأمن المعلومات و\r\nوالبرمجيات والبيانات بما في ذلك البرامج  IOT, ومنصات IOT, وأجهزة الاستشعار والمعدات استنادا الى (IOT) إنترنت الأشياء\r\nالتحليلية والتعلم العميق وخوارزمية التعلم الآلي والبرمجيات وتحليل الأمن السيبراني الشامل والاستماع السلبي والتدخل النشط وأي , واختبار الاختراق (MDS) تكامل مع جميع البرامج والمعدات وخدمات البنية التحتية للمفاتيح العمومية وخدمات الكشف المدارة\r\nوخدمات التدريب والاستشارات.\r\n\r\nتتميز شبكات الكهرباء اليوم بحجمها وتعقيدها بالإضافة إلى التقنيات والتقنيات الجديدة نظمة الطاقة وإدارة المشاريع -3\r\nلإنتاج ونقل وتوزيع وحماية وقياس الطاقة. يمكن أن تعمل أنظمة الطاقة هذه بمستويات جهد عالية أو متوسطة أو منخفضة. الأنظمة الكهربائية ، والتوربينات اللازمة لإنتاج الكهرباء ، وجميع معدات التحويل والمحولات اللازمة للنقل والتوزيع ، من المولدات ، ومجموعة واسعة من المنتجات والخدمات مع جميع البنية التحتية التكنولوجية وأنظمة التحكم مطلوب لحماية الأنظمة والتحكم فيها.\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20About.png)', 'pages/October2019/yrZYkEM9vtHDdPkn4Rl9.PNG', 'معلومات-عنا', 'معلومات عنا', 'معلومات عنا', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-29 10:42:18', '2020-11-11 15:02:21', 'ar', NULL, NULL),
(12, 2, 'Aperçu l Kontrolmatik', 'Aperçu', 'Kontrolmatik propose des services complets pour accompagner ses clients tout au long du cycle de vie, de leurs actifs du concept au démentalement, en passant par les marchés de l’énergie, du transport, des mines, processus et des services publices.\nCouplé  à une curiosité et une soif sans fin pour de nouvelles idées pour aider nos clients à résoudre leurs problèmes commerciaux, nous avons une culture de l’amélioration et des meilleures pratiques qui infuse toutes nos opérations.\n\n**Les endroits :**\n\n* Quartiers généraux à Istanbul (Usines et Bureaux principaux) \n  * Dubai ( Bureau de vente )\n  * Ethiopie ( Bureau de vente et atelier )\n  * Allemagne ( Bureau de vente )\n  * Soudan ( Atelier )\n  * Kenya ( Bureau de vente )\n  * Kazakhestan ( Bureau de vente )\n* Réalisé de nombreux projets dans plus que 20 pays différents\n\nKontrolmatik a plusieurs partenariats avec un des leaders mondiaux dans plusieurs industries comme: **ABB, GE, SIMENS, OSI SOFT, NOZOMI NETWORKS, HUWAIE, BELDEN, HIRSCMANN, TOFINO, and CSIA.**', 'pages\\August2019\\LUuTFBd2ptQb3KCEyIOA.png', 'apercu', 'Aperçu', 'Aperçu', 'INACTIVE', '2019-07-26 06:40:53', '2020-02-23 09:44:36', 'fr', '', NULL),
(13, 2, 'نظرة عامة', 'نظرة عامة', 'نظرة عامة\r\n\r\n خدمات شاملة في أسواق مختلفة مثل الطاقة والنقل والتعدين والعمليات والخدمات العامة ، Kontrolmatik \r\nتقدم \r\nللتوقف عن هذا المفهوم ، لدعم عملائها في دورة الحياة الكاملة لأصول عملائهم.\r\n\r\nتم وضع أسس كونترولماتيك عندما اجتمع ثلاثة رواد أعمال شباب ، سامي أصلانهان وعمر أونسالان وصلاح الدين كارتال لتحقيق مُثلهم العليا في **\r\n\r\n 2007 **. سامي أصلانهان ، أحد الشركاء الذين درسوا الهندسة الإلكترونية والاتصالات, يبلغ من İkitelli İstoç العمر 26 عامًا عندما أسس الشركة كمكتب وورشة تصنيع اللوحات في \r\n\r\nأول عمل تم تحويله إلى شركة كونترولماتيك ، والذي تم تأسيسه في يناير **  2008 \r\n\r\n- أتمتة المباني ونظام التيار الضعيف Microsoft إلى فاتورة هو مشروع مبنى المكتب الرئيسي لشركة \r\nمع هذا المشروع والخبرة المكتسبة من الشركة التي عملوا بها من قبل للأتمتة والعديد من المشاريع في تركيا ، أكملوا أعمال وهي أول شركة أجنبية ، تم توقيعها في يناير 2008 مرة أخرى معZagalata  Airport أتمتة \r\n\r\nمبنى مطار أذربيجان\r\n\r\nالثقة والعلاقات التي توفرها في هذه المجالات. بعد هذا العمل ، واصلوا العمل في الخارج في ليبيا ، مطار سرت ، في أذربيجان ، قصر حيدر علييف الرئاسي ، وأتمتة البناء وأعمال الكهرباء.\r\n\r\nفي ** 2010 ** وقعت Kontrolmatik', 'pages\\August2019\\LUuTFBd2ptQb3KCEyIOA.png', 'نظرة-عامة', 'نظرة عامة', 'نظرة عامة', 'INACTIVE', '2019-07-26 06:40:53', '2020-11-11 15:08:45', 'ar', NULL, NULL),
(14, 3, 'SECURITEE l Kontrolmatik', 'SECURITEE', 'La sécurité est plus qu’une politique manuelle ou une vidéo de formation, c’est notre façon de travailler et notre mode de 24/7.\nKontrolmatik vous invite à faire l’éxperience de notre culture de soins. Une culture dans laquelle est la sécurité, la santé et le bien-être, qui sont des priorités absolues et dans lesquelles nous sommes tous responsables de la recherche des autres.\n\nLa culture de sécurité de kontrolmatik s’étend en dehors des murs des bureaux, au-dela du site de projet et dans nos voitures, nos maisons et nos communautés, affectant toutes les personnes avec lesquelles nous integrissons partout dans le monde. C’est à propos de chacun de nous de faire la sécurité une valeur personnelle avec laquelle nous vivons chaque jour.\n', 'pages\\August2019\\KAPebwk5SwiHRrnW0fj9.jpg', 'securitee', 'SECURITEE', 'SECURITEE', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 08:54:37', '2020-02-23 09:45:07', 'fr', '', NULL),
(15, 3, 'السلامة', 'السلامة', 'السلامة أكثرمن دليل السياسات أو فيديو التدريب, هذه هي الطريقة التي نؤدي بها أعمالنا و كيف نعيش لمدة      7/24 \n  .KONTROLMATIK تدعوكم لتجربة ثقافتنا في الرعاية – ثقافة في السلامة, الصحة و الحياة الاجتماعية هي من أولوياتنا الكبرى,\nو تحمل مسؤولية الاهتمام الى بعضنا البعض.\n\nتمتد ثقافة سلامة  KONTROLMATIK  خارج جدران المكتب, ما وراء موقع المشاريع, و سياراتنا, منازلنا و مجتمعانتا, و تؤثر على جميع الاشخاص الذين نتعامل معهم في كل مكان حول العالم, و كل واحد منا يجعل السلامة قيمة شخصية نعيشها كل يوم.', 'pages\\August2019\\KAPebwk5SwiHRrnW0fj9.jpg', 'السلامة', 'السلامة', 'السلامة', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 08:54:37', '2019-10-17 09:37:15', 'ar', '', NULL),
(16, 4, 'NOS AVANTAGES l Kontrolmatik', 'NOS AVANTAGES', 'L’innovation est un moteur de notre activité, le besoin d’améliorer les personnes, processus et la technologie, et nous cherchons toujours de meilleures façons de livrer pour le bénéfice de nos clients et de notre entreprise.\n\nChez kontrolmatik, nous apportons de nouvelles idées à chaque projet. Notre volonté d’améliorer continuellement les performances au sein de notre organisation.\n\nL’élément clé de notre culture, l’innovation s’applique à nos employés, à nos processus et à nos technologies, ce qui nous pousse à améliorer nos performances et à rechercher constamment des opportunités pour faire progresser notre entreprise.\n\nNotre gamme de services en constante évolution, apporte de nouvelles et passionnantes connexions aux technologies et aux méthodes qui ouvrent la voie à nos activités. Nous tirons parti des meilleures pratiques de l’industrie dans des dizaines de marchés répartis sur des centaines de sites pour proposer de nouvelles approches et nouvelles solutions.', 'pages\\August2019\\QE6YXoTxtHckB0uUDnYL.jpg', 'nos-avantages', 'NOS AVANTAGES', 'NOS AVANTAGES', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 08:58:58', '2020-02-23 09:46:02', 'fr', '', NULL),
(17, 4, 'ايجابياتنا', 'ايجابياتنا', 'ايجابياتنا\r\nالابتكار هو القوة الدافعة في أعمالنا ، والحاجة إلى تحسين يمتد ليشمل الأفراد والعمليات والتكنولوجيا ونحن نبحث دائمًا عن طرق أفضل لتقديمها لصالح عملائنا وأعمالنا.\r\n\r\n\r\nأفكارًا جديدة لكل مشروع. يعمل دافعنا للتحسين المستمر في جميع أنحاء مؤسستنا.  Kontrolmatik في\r\nجزء أساسي من ثقافتنا ، ينطبق الابتكار على موظفينا وعملياتنا وتقنياتنا ؛ مما يدفعنا لأداء أفضل والبحث باستمرار عن فرص لدفع أعمالنا إلى الأمام.\r\n\r\nتوفر مجموعة خدماتنا المتزايدة روابط جديدة ومثيرة للتقنيات والأساليب التي تقود الطريق عبر أعمالنا. نستفيد من أفضل الممارسات الصناعية الأوسع نطاقًا في عشرات الأسواق عبر مئات المواقع لتقديم أساليب جديدة وحلول جديدة.\r\n\r\n![](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/pages/Kontrolmatik%20Advantages%20Resize%2060.jpg)', 'pages\\August2019\\QE6YXoTxtHckB0uUDnYL.jpg', 'ايجابياتنا', 'ايجابياتنا', 'ايجابياتنا', 'INACTIVE', '2019-08-06 08:58:58', '2020-11-11 15:32:06', 'ar', NULL, NULL),
