(2, 12, 3, 'Bursa Gas Insulated Switchgear 154/34,5 kV Substation Bursa/Türkiye', 'Bursa Gas Insulated Switchgear 154/34,5 kV Substation Bursa/Türkiye', NULL, '* Bursa substation, which was built in 1967, is a substation where Bursa\'s important energy needs are met in terms of location and location. In this context, the old system was insufficient in terms of operation, reliability and power. 3 temporary prefabricated containers were placed on the land behind the existing 34.5 kV old type switchgear building until the GIS center was built. Relay, control AC, DC distribution panels are manufactured by us in the container whose projects and approvals have been obtained and installed. After the assembly, the cable pulls between the old feeders and the panels, the necessary safety precautions were taken, and the feeder feeder was transferred by making the test and commissioning studies with a minimum of power cuts. The 154 kV substation was transported in a period of 1 week and was completed with a minimum of power failure. The 34.5 kV old type open switchgear was transferred to the temporary feeder center without leaving the city without power. \r\n* For the new 154 kV Gas insulated switchgear building, the old transformer maintenance and control building was demolished and the building was constructed to be 3 live and 1 spare power transformer hall according to TEİAŞ specifications. After construction works and landscaping; 154 kV Sieyuan brand 3 lines, 1 cable, 4 transformers, 1 coupling, 1 spare line feeder GIS. Protection, control panel design, secondary project design, AC, DC distribution panels, server and automation panels of 34.5 kV 42 metalclad cells, the most suitable resonance found by the device by automatic scanning depending on the capacity of the system in the TEİAŞ specifications (in IEC 62271 standards). Gas insulated switchgear high voltage tests were carried out by applying frequency-tested 270 kV AC voltage. Turkey also established so that it can run smoothly for the first time IEC61850 communication protocol has been under the Micro-SCADA system energy centers after our expert team of engineers and test Commissioning work.\r\n#### Our work in the Substation, \r\n* 154 kV old system transported to temporary containers and commissioning,\r\n* GIS 3 lines, 1 cable, 4 transformers, 1 cubicle, 1 spare line feeder complete test commissioning\r\n*  SF6 Gas quality measurement\r\n* Breaker disconnector contact resistance tests,\r\n* Circuit Breaker opening and closing time tests\r\n* Current transformer, voltage transformer ratio polarity\r\n* GIS, LCC function tests\r\n* IEC 61850 Micro scada system installation, commissioning\r\n* GIS AC high voltage tests at 270 kV voltage level (IEC 62271)\r\n* Project drawings\r\n* Control relay, AC, DC distribution panel manufacturing\r\n* Rehabilitation works\r\n * Material approvals,\r\n* 34,5 kV medium voltage Metalclad test and commissioning,', 'Bursa, Turkey', 'Engineering, Project Desing, High Voltage Energy Management System, SCADA, Control and Protection Panels, High Voltage Cable and GIS Test, Test and Commissioning,', 'posts/May2020/nVV6rrW05FQ8DPzhYxjb.jpg', '[\"posts\\/May2020\\/AU6FgxZeFfG7Z27pkVRh.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/AKELMIFUvVbZsiqi68Hs.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/a3uWv2KLJXJ5GnIQhiuv.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/uk7S0s9cl2K8BGhsfqYL.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/HkzI97rLeD0fbusnP65i.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/rUTfnFQxGgigTNZcGVGp.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/YnDDshYJ0X6eHJEBVOkE.jpg\"]', 'posts/May2020/YQJqCHGK04kc1hoGB7VO.jpg', 'bursa-gas-insulated-switchgear-154-34-5-kv-substation-bursa-turkiye', 'Bursa Gas Insulated Switchgear 154/34,5 kV Substation Bursa/Türkiye', 'Bursa Gas Insulated Switchgear 154/34,5 kV Substation Bursa/Türkiye', 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-08-06 11:08:17', '2020-05-08 08:29:57', 22, 'en'),
