(4, 8, 3, 'ICDAS Bekirli I&S Factory 600 MW Thermal Power Plant', 'ICDAS Bekirli I&S Factory 600 MW Thermal Power Plant', NULL, 'The following items are implemented for a gas turbine (600 MW)\r\n\r\n  * Reactive Power Control\r\n  * Primary Frequency Control\r\n  * Secondary Frequency Control\r\n  * Power Factor Control\r\n  * 154KV Main Feeder Voltage Control\r\n  * CSV File Report to\r\n  * Data Analysis\r\n\r\nAnd also, mathematical models and PSS tests of İçdaş Energy Bekirli 600 mW Power Plant are carried out in the scope of this project.\r\n\r\nPreliminary studies for 600 MW Bekirli Power Plant Generator excitation system PSS tests, generator for the power plant, mathematical model for exciter and the avr, PSS (Power System Stabilizier) set and performance tests are all implemented with Load Dispatch Department of European Transmission Coordination Directorate and TUBITAK.', 'Bekirli, Turkey', NULL, 'posts\\August2019\\nNRacSD8Wty5lG7dQTbS.jpg', '[\"posts\\\\August2019\\\\a0xUt2VKAZODbOOJDoOC.jpg\",\"posts\\\\August2019\\\\8knKC9UNGy7x2g1VPAiz.jpg\",\"posts\\\\August2019\\\\OztTsRvd4rBNxFiqY8pe.jpg\"]', 'posts\\August2019\\20jrRiY8tKdNvFe1vC9g.png', 'icdas-bekirli-iands-factory-600-mw-thermal-power-plant', 'ICDAS Bekirli I&S Factory 600 MW Thermal Power Plant', 'ICDAS Bekirli I&S Factory 600 MW Thermal Power Plant', 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-08-08 10:53:33', '2020-05-07 18:37:18', 21, 'en'),
