(322, 8, 3, 'Nigeria Kwale Refinery Gas Plant Flaredown Rehabilitation Project', 'Nigeria Kwale Refinery Gas Plant Flaredown Rehabilitation Project', 'Nigeria Kwale Refinery Gas Plant Flaredown Rehabilitation Project', '**PROJECT PURPOSE**\r\n\r\nThe Nigerian Agip Oil Company Limited (NAOC) and ENI are the end users.\r\nThe Kwale Gas Plant  was upgraded with the aim to gather the associated and presently flared gas and deliver it to Ob/Ob(Obiafu/Obrikom) Gas Plant via the existing 24’’ Kwale-Ob/Ob gas pipeline. The Kwale Flaredown Project was developed taking into consideration the future upgrading / expansion phases to minimize interference.  The work covered by this project was the minimum required to realize the flaredown objective and process automation of the plant only.\r\nThe Kwale Flaredown Project was involving the upgrading of the existing Kwale Gas Plant in order to recover the Associated Gas (AG) (about 10MMSCFD) currently flared to the MP gas header and then for delivery as fuel gas via the existing Kwale Gas pipeline to Ob/Ob (Obiafu/Obrokom) Gas Plant. The project objectives was achieved primarily by the addition of Compression Facilities and associated utilities at Kwale Gas Plant.\r\n\r\nThe objectives of the Kwale Flaredown Project were:\r\n\r\n•	To collect the associated gas and deliver it into the existing Kwale Gas Pipeline to Ob/Ob Gas Plant via MP Header.\r\n•	To implement the “Flaring down” Policy.\r\n\r\n**PROJECT SCOPE**\r\n\r\nUnder the Kontrolmatik scope, electrical systems rehabilitation of Gas Flare Down System was executed.\r\nThe scope of works was covering the following systems design, manufacturing and supply for Kwale Gas Flare Down System. \r\n\r\n**DETAILED SCOPE OF SUPPLY**\r\n\r\n* High Voltage (HV) Switchgear\r\n* Low Voltage (LV) Switchgear ASP\r\n* Low Voltage (LV) Switchgear\r\n* 11 kV Circuit Breaker\r\n* Interconnecting Panel\r\n* High Voltage Power Transformer\r\n* Compressor Motor Control Cabinet (MCC) \r\n* DC Accumulator Batteries\r\n* DC Systems\r\n* UPS and Battery Charger\r\n* Low Voltage Circuit Breaker\r\n\r\n**FOR ABOVE WRITTEN SYSTEMS BELOW SERVICES WERE PROVIDED UNDER KONTROLMATİK**\r\n\r\n**ENGINEERING**\r\n\r\n* Technical Datasheet of Each Package\r\n* Inspection Datasheet\r\n* Design and Engineering\r\n* Quality Plan of Manufacturing Testing and Inspection\r\n* Production Schedule\r\n* Local Support Capability Specification\r\n* Inspection Test Plan\r\n* Storage Procedure\r\n\r\n**PROCUREMENT, MANUFACTURING, ASSEMBLY & PAINTING**\r\n\r\n* Manufacturing \r\n* Procurement of Components and Sub-Components\r\n* Fabrication and Assembly\r\n* Painting\r\n* Special Tools for Installation and Maintenance\r\n* Installation and Pre-Commisioning Spares\r\n\r\n**SUPPLY & DELIVERY AS PER SCOPE OF WORK**\r\n\r\n* Certifications including Full Traceability\r\n* Inspection and Tests\r\n* Documentation \r\n* Quality Assurance/ Quality Control (QA/QC)', 'Nigeria', NULL, 'posts/May2020/3A7ZGBCXiguARaCH67rZ.jpg', '[\"posts\\/May2020\\/e0xqCbBYNNO0K69lrR7r.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/mWI4D61dvr1d2u6l87Mx.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/EzpNJmq8wuYP2koAbH2v.jpeg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/vr6fNW54r1yFHsCZoEnx.jpeg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/fJyFH5yFmo2OzZ5URJIk.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/wWMZDBF9tO6Y6RV6KpZt.jpeg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/bVFPEaTgmZ1QbDxIH1bg.jpeg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/RcHbIEz9RE5j3l3RHAA1.jpg\"]', 'posts/May2020/GdpNajAVz4W6p9xPl6eT.jpg', 'nigeria-kwale-refinery-gas-plant-flaredown-rehabilitation-project', 'Nigeria Kwale Refinery Gas Plant Flaredown Rehabilitation Project', 'High Voltage (HV) Switchgear\r\nLow Voltage (LV) Switchgear ASP\r\nLow Voltage (LV) Switchgear\r\n11 kV Circuit Breaker\r\nInterconnecting Panel\r\nHigh Voltage Power Transformer\r\nCompressor Motor Control Cabinet (MCC) \r\nDC Accumulator Batteries\r\nDC Systems\r\nUPS and Battery Charger\r\nLow Voltage Circuit Breaker\r\nNigeria, oil&gas, Refinery', 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2020-05-07 15:27:43', '2020-05-09 19:16:58', 24, 'en'),
