upports, all cable supporting systems within 110 kV line feeder extension area\r\n* Low voltage and control cables PVC insulated without armor control & LV power cables of 110 kV Line Feeder extension area including termination & accessories\r\n* Relay protection panel 110kV\r\n* Busbar protection panel integration to existing BBP system\r\n* Control panel 110kV \r\n* Marshalling Kiosk 110 kV \r\n* RTU/SCADA SYSTEM Integration of 110 kV Line Bay to Existing RTU/ SCADA System of Nejrab Substation', 'Afghanistan', NULL, 'posts/May2020/nsyCLN1zF0Eb7exXt0Tf.jpg', '[\"posts\\/May2020\\/sLawq2jaIYQBh7YEJyaC.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/f3j6e4VVKHQZQl8xvulN.jpg\",\"posts\\/May2020\\/UCKpQIo7vi5uJERM5vdZ.jpg\"]', 'posts/May2020/leGD1HuJabGPEXPJxVrA.jpg', 'afghanistan-nejrab-110-kv-substation-and-line-bay-poject', 'Afghanistan Nejrab 110 kV Substation and Line Bay Poject', 'High Voltage Line,\r\nSubstation, Disconnector, Circuit Breaker, SCADA, Protection, Control', 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2020-05-07 16:36:15', '2020-05-09 19:31:18', 22, 'en'),
