(31, 6, 'توزيع ونقل الطاقة', 'EPC Substation Subulated Gas Insulated **(GIS) ** أو معزول بالهواء ** (AIS)**\r\n\r\n*التركيب الميكانيكي وشراء الصلب والأجهزة والمحولات\r\n\r\n* التركيبات الكهربائية والتركيب\r\n\r\n*كل الإنتاج الثانوي والهندسة والتكليف\r\n\r\n*أنظمة الحماية واختبارات الأداء الميدانية الأولية / الثانوية\r\n\r\n* **حتى 500 كيلو فولت ** محطة فرعية ذات جهد عالي\r\n1-40،5* **  كيلو فولت أنظمة جهد متوسطة ** \r\n\r\n* **كيلو فولت 0،4 ** أنظمة الجهد المنخفض\r\n\r\n**تفاصيل**\r\nتصميم وتحليل أنظمة القوى*\r\n\r\nتحليل ماس كهربائى*\r\n\r\nتحليل تدفق الحمل ، تحميل - سفك*\r\n\r\nتحليل الاستقرار ، استقرار الانتقال ، استقرار الجهد*\r\n\r\nتنسيق التتابع ، تحليل الانتقائية*\r\n\r\nالتحليل التوافقي ، تحليل الانتقال الكهرومغناطيسي*\r\n\r\nتصميم أنظمة القوى*\r\n\r\nجودة الشبكة وأعمال الربط*\r\n\r\nتنظيم التردد*\r\n\r\nاستقرار نظام الطاقة*\r\n\r\nالنمذجة الرياضية لمحطات الطاقة*\r\n\r\nالمعدات الأولية: المحول ، قاطع الدائرة ، الفاصل ، المحول الحالي ، محول الجهد ، مانع الصواعق ،*\r\n\r\nتركيب ميكانيكي*\r\n\r\nأعمال الصلب*\r\n\r\nأعمال مدنية*\r\n\r\nSCADA حلول الطاقة  *\r\n\r\nحل إدارة التوزيع*\r\n\r\nIEC 61850 وتطبيقات الاتصالات*\r\n\r\nتحليل ونمذجة جودة الطاقة*\r\n\r\n وحلول الاتصالات TEİAŞ RTU محطات توليد الكهرباء  *\r\n\r\nTEİAŞ محطات توليد الطاقة حلول الخدمات المساعدة *\r\n\r\n(التحكم في التردد الأساسي والثانوي ، التحكم في القدرة التفاعلية) *\r\n\r\nالمحطات الفرعية. مشروع ثانوي ، مرحل ، لوحة ، و*\r\n\r\nالكهربة والكابلات*\r\n\r\nحلول لوحة حماية التحكم*\r\n\r\nالخدمات التي نقدمها لمحطات توليد الطاقة*\r\n\r\nتصميم وشراء أنظمة التحكم*\r\n\r\nالتصميم المعماري لأنظمة التحكم*\r\n\r\nاختيار المعدات لأنظمة التحكم*\r\n\r\nتصميم وتصنيع لوحات التحكم*\r\n\r\nتوريد لوحات الأجهزة والبرامج*\r\n\r\nتنفيذ أنظمة التحكم*\r\n\r\nPLC / DCS برمجة  *\r\n\r\nتكوين الأجهزة / البرامج*\r\n\r\nHMI / وحدة التحكم هندسة *\r\n\r\nFAT (اختبارات قبول المصنع) *\r\n\r\nبدء التشغيل والتكليف*\r\n\r\nSAT (اختبارات قبول الموقع) *\r\n\r\nالتكليف*\r\n\r\nخدمات ميدانية*\r\n\r\nمخططات الكابلات الحلقية*', NULL, 'توزيع-ونقل-الطاقة', '[]', '2020-05-03 17:06:16', '2020-11-09 15:13:50', 'ar'),
(33, 6, 'Elektrik Dağıtımı ve İletimi', '**Güç Dağıtımı ve İletimi için verdiğimiz hizmetler:**\r\n\r\n* EPC - Anahtar Teslim Trafo Merkezi- Gaz İzoleli (GIS) ya da Hava İzoleli (Açık şalt) (AIS)\r\n* Elektrik, Mekanik ve İnşaat Detay Tasarımı\r\n* Çelik, Aparat ve Transformatörlerin Mekanik Kurulumu ve Tedariki\r\n* Elektrik Tesisatı ve Montajı\r\n* Tüm İkincil Üretim ve Mühendislik ve Devreye Alma\r\n* Koruma Sistemleri ve Birincil / İkincil saha performans testleri\r\n* 500 KV\'a kadar YÜKSEK Gerilim Trafo Merkezi\r\n* 36-40,5 KV ORTA Gerilim Sistemleri\r\n* 0,4 KV ALÇAK Gerilim Sistemleri  \r\n\r\n* Güç sistemlerinin tasarımı ve analizi\r\n* Kısa devre analizi\r\n* Yük akışı analizi, yük atma\r\n* Kararlılık analizi, geçiş kararlılığı, gerilim kararlılığı\r\n* Röle koordinasyonu, seçicilik analizi\r\n* Harmonik analiz, elektromanyetik geçiş analizi\r\n* Güç sistemlerinin tasarımı\r\n* Şebeke kalitesi, arabağlantı çalışmaları\r\n* Frekans regülasyonu\r\n* Güç sistemi kararlılığı\r\n* Enerji santrallerinin matematiksel modellenmesi\r\n\r\n* Ekipman Tedariği: Transformatör, Devre Kesici, Ayırıcı, Akım Trafosu, Gerilim Trafosu, Parafudr,Orta Gerilim Hücre\r\n* Mekanik Montaj\r\n* Çelik İşleri\r\n* İnşaat işleri\r\n* Enerji SCADA çözümleri\r\n* Dağıtım Yönetim Sistemi (DMS) Çözümü\r\n* IEC 61850 ve iletişim uygulamaları\r\n* Güç kalitesi analizi ve modellemesi\r\n* Enerji santralleri TEİAŞ RTU ve iletişim çözümleri\r\n* Enerji santralleri TEİAŞ yardımcı hizmet çözümleri\r\n* (Birincil ve ikincil frekans kontrolü, reaktif güç kontrolü)\r\n* Substationlar; ikincil proje, geçiş, panel ve\r\n* Elektrifikasyon, Kablolama\r\n* Kontrol Koruma Paneli Çözümleri\r\n* Enerji üretim tesisleri için verdiğimiz hizmetler\r\n* Kontrol sistemlerinin tasarımı ve tedariki\r\n* Kontrol sistemlerinin mimari tasarımı\r\n* Kontrol sistemlerinin ekipman seçimi\r\n* Kontrol panellerinin tasarımı ve üretimi\r\n* Donanım ve yazılım panellerinin temini\r\n* Kontrol sistemlerinin uygulanması\r\n* PLC / DCS programlama\r\n* Donanım / yazılım yapılandırması\r\n* HMI / konsol mühendisliği\r\n* FAT (fabrika kabul testleri)\r\n* Devreye alma ve devreye alma\r\n* SAT (saha kabul testleri)\r\n* Saha hizmetleri\r\n* Döngü kablolama şemaları', NULL, 'elektrik-dagitimi-ve-iletimi', '[{\"download_link\":\"sector\\/May2020\\/eQCuMW9Wcsl8ExegBa2j.png\",\"original_name\":\"logo-sv.png\"}]', '2020-05-03 17:06:48', '2020-05-12 07:37:30', 'tr'),
(34, 7, 'Process Industry Sector l Kontrolmatik', 'Kontrolmatik has broad knowledge and experience with international standards which underlie at the design and execution of the installations in the process industry.\r\n\r\nProven processing capabilities are in the following products and services:\r\n\r\n*  Electrical design, supply and implementation\r\n*  Piping and mechanical detailed design\r\n*  BOP (Balance of Plant)- Motors,Drive,Pumps,Valves etc.\r\n*  Mechanical and electrical installation\r\n*  Electrification\r\n*  Instrumentation\r\n*  Process control solutions (PLC, DCS,SCADA)\r\n*  Plant Information (PI) systems\r\n*  Manufacturing Execution Systems (MES)\r\n*  Compact command center solutions\r\n*  Mobile data center solutions\r\n\r\n[Kontrolmatik EPCM Brochure (ENG) ](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/brochures/April2020/vvw5eOX722FxcEBUfk5e.pdf)', NULL, 'process-industry', NULL, '2020-05-03 17:07:44', '2020-05-04 05:08:39', 'en'),
(35, 7, 'Processus Industriel Secteur l Kontrolmatik', '**Services que nous fournissons pour l\'industrie des procédés:**\r\n\r\nL’expérience impressionnante de Kontrolmatik dans ce secteur comprend des travaux d’électrification à haute valeur ajoutée pour les industries de transformation suivantes;\r\n\r\n* Industrie chimique et pharmaceutique\r\n* Nourriture et boisson\r\n* Industrie agro-alimentaire\r\n* Pétrochimie et polymères\r\n\r\nL\'entreprise possède une vaste connaissance et une grande expérience des normes internationales qui sous-tendent la conception et l\'exécution des installations dans l\'industrie des procédés.\r\n\r\nLes capacités de traitement éprouvées se trouvent dans les produits et services suivants:\r\n\r\n* Conception électrique, fourniture et mise en œuvre\r\n* Tuyauterie et conception détaillée mécanique\r\n* BOP (Balance of Plant)\r\n* Installation mécanique et électrique\r\n* Instrumentation\r\n* Solutions de contrôle de processus (PLC, DCS)\r\n* Systèmes d\'information sur les plantes (PI)\r\n* Systèmes d\'exécution de fabrication (MES)\r\n* Solutions de centre de commande compactes\r\n* Solutions de centres de données mobiles', 'sector\\September2019\\43P65y6gmbQZQBUKqvAi.png', 'installations-industrielles', '[]', '2019-08-05 08:54:03', '2020-06-22 05:59:09', 'fr'),
(36, 7, 'صناعة المعالجة', '**الخدمات التي نقدمها لصناعة المعالجة:**\r\n\r\n الرائع في هذا القطاع أعمال كهربة عالية القيمة المضافة للصناعات العملية التالية ؛ Kontrolmatik  يتضمن سجل\r\nصناعة الكيماويات والأدوية*\r\n\r\nالأغذية والمشروبات*\r\n\r\nالصناعات الزراعية*\r\n\r\nالبتروكيماويات والبوليمرات*\r\n\r\nتتمتع الشركة بمعرفة وخبرة واسعة فيما يتعلق بالمعايير الدولية التي تكمن وراء تصميم وتنفيذ التركيبات في صناعة العمليات\r\n\r\n: تتوفر إمكانات المعالجة المؤكدة في المنتجات والخدمات التالية\r\n\r\nالتصميم الكهربائي والتوريد والتنفيذ*\r\n\r\nتصميم مفصل للأنابيب والميكانيكية*\r\n\r\nBOP (ميزان النبات) *\r\n\r\nالتركيبات الميكانيكية والكهربائية*\r\n\r\nالأجهزة*\r\n\r\nحلول التحكم في العمليات (PLC ، DCS) *\r\n\r\nأنظمة معلومات المصنع (PI) *\r\n\r\nأنظمة تنفيذ التصنيع (MES) *\r\n\r\nحلول مركز القيادة المدمجة*\r\n\r\nحلول مراكز البيانات المتنقلة*', NULL, 'صناعة-المعالجة', '[]', '2020-05-03 17:08:49', '2020-11-09 14:42:34', 'ar'),
(37, 7, 'Proses Endüstrisi', '**Proses Endüstrisi için verdiğimiz hizmetler:** \r\nKontrolmatik sektördeki etkileyici performansı sayesinde aşağıdaki proses endüstrileri için katma değeri yüksek yazılım, kontrol sistemi, elektrifikasyon ve enstrümantasyon çözümleri üretmektedir.\r\n* Kimya Ve İlaç Endüstrisi \r\n* Yiyecek Ve İçecek \r\n* Tarımsal Sanayi \r\n* Petrokimyasallar Ve Polimerler \r\n\r\nŞirket, proses endüstrisinde tasarım ve uygulamanın temelini oluşturan uluslararası standartlar hakkında geniş bilgi ve deneyime sahiptir. Kanıtlanmış tasarım,montaj ve proje yönetimi yetenekleri ile aşağıdaki ürün ve hizmetler için geniş ölçekli çözümler bulundurmaktadır:\r\n* Elektrik Sistemi Tasarımı, Tedariği, Montajı Ve Uygulaması \r\n* Borulama Ve Mekanik Detay Tasarımı \r\n* BOP (Balance Of Plant) \r\n* Mekanik Ve Elektrik Tesisatı \r\n* Enstrümantasyon \r\n* Proses Kontrol Çözümleri (PLC, DCS) \r\n* Tesis Bilgi Sistemleri(PI) \r\n* Üretim Yönetim Sistemleri (MES) \r\n* Kompakt Kumanda Merkezi Çözümleri \r\n* Mobil Veri Merkezi Çözümleri', NULL, 'proses-endustrisi', '[{\"download_link\":\"sector\\/May2020\\/4aPJEKHjz19IuWdjz8dx.pdf\",\"original_name\":\"EPCM Brochure(TR).pdf\"}]', '2020-05-03 17:09:23', '2021-02-24 16:27:10', 'tr'),
(38, 8, 'Oil & Gas Sector l Kontrolmatik', 'Kontrolmatik with his solution partners provides entire electrification, instrumentation and automation solutions in oil refineries industry and gained experience in the refineries different operation units.\r\n\r\n*  Atmospheric/vacuum crude units\r\n*  Visbreaking\r\n*  Reforming (Conventional and CCR)\r\n*  Hydrodesulpherization\r\n*  FCCU\r\n*  Sulphur recovery and TGT\r\n*  Alkylation\r\n*  Isomerization\r\n*  Dimersol unit\r\n*  Tank farm and blending\r\n*  LPG storage unloading/loading stations\r\n*  Gas flare down\r\n*  Utilities and others\r\n\r\nWe have successfully implemented electrification,\r\ninstrumentation and control new, modernization or\r\nrevamp projects of entire refineries and gas industries in\r\nseveral countries.\r\n\r\nKontrolmatik offers specific know-how in:\r\n\r\n*  EI&C systems as EPC\r\n*  Tank farm design, including sophisticated controls and monitoring systems\r\n*  Advanced control of refinery units using multi variable predictive constraint control algorithms\r\n*  SIL 3 Degree F&G and ESD Systems\r\n*  Gas storage facilities, off- gas compression\r\n*  Natural Gas Pipeline transportation and distribution stations\r\n*  Cyber security\r\n*  Anti-intrusion and heat detection systems', NULL, 'oil-gas', NULL, '2020-05-03 17:10:24', '2020-05-04 05:08:21', 'en'),
(39, 8, 'Pétrole Et Gaz Secteur l Kontrolmatik', 'Kontrolmatik avec ses partenaires de solutions fournit des solutions d\'électrification, d\'instrumentation et d\'automatisation complètes dans l\'industrie des raffineries de pétrole et a acquis une expérience dans les différentes unités d\'exploitation des raffineries.\r\n\r\n* Unités de brut atmosphérique / sous vide\r\n* Visbreaking\r\n* Réforme (conventionnelle et CCR)\r\n* Hydrodésulfuration\r\n* FCCU\r\n* Récupération du soufre et TGT\r\n* Alkylation\r\n* Isomérisation\r\n* Unité Dimersol\r\n* Parc de stockage et mélange\r\n* Stations de déchargement / chargement de stockage de LPG\r\n* Flambée de gaz vers le bas\r\n* Utilitaires et autres\r\nNous avons mis en œuvre avec succès l\'électrification,\r\ninstrumentation et contrôle nouveaux, modernisation ou\r\nréorganiser des projets de raffineries entières et des industries du gaz\r\nplusieurs pays.\r\n\r\nKontrolmatik propose un savoir-faire spécifique en:\r\n\r\n* Systèmes EI&C comme EPC\r\n* Conception de parcs de stockage, y compris des systèmes de contrôle et de surveillance sophistiqués\r\n* Contrôle avancé des unités de raffinerie à l\'aide d\'algorithmes de contrôle de contraintes prédictives multi variables\r\n* Systèmes SIL 3 degrés F&G et ESD\r\n* Installations de stockage de gaz, compression des effluents gazeux\r\n* Stations de transport et de distribution de gazoducs\r\n*  La cyber-sécurité\r\n* Systèmes anti-intrusion et détection de chaleur', NULL, 'petrole-et-gaz', '[]', '2020-06-12 05:26:11', '2020-06-22 05:59:58', 'fr'),
(40, 8, 'النفط والغاز الطبيعي', 'مع شركائه في الحلول حلولاً كاملة للكهرباء ، والأجهزة ، والأتمتة في صناعة مصافي النفط ، Kontrolmatik يوفر\r\nواكتسبوا خبرة في وحدات التشغيل المختلفة للمصافي\r\n\r\nوحدات الخام الجوية / الفراغية*\r\n\r\nتكسير اللزوجة*\r\n\r\n(CCR التقليدي و) الإصلاح *\r\n\r\nنزع الكبريت المائي*\r\n\r\nFCCU*\r\n\r\nTGTاسترداد الكبريت و*\r\n\r\nالألكلة*\r\n\r\nالأزمرة*\r\n\r\nوحدة ديميرسول*\r\n\r\nخزان المزرعة والخلط*\r\n\r\nمحطات تفريغ / تحميل تخزين غاز البترول المسال*\r\n\r\nاشتعال الغاز*\r\n\r\nالمرافق وغيرها*\r\n\r\n\r\nلقد نجحنا في تنفيذ الكهرباء والأجهزة والتحكم في مشاريع جديدة أو تحديث أو تجديد لمصافي تكرير بأكملها وصناعات الغاز في العديد من البلدان\r\n  خبرة محددة في Kontrolmatik تقدم\r\nEPC مثل EI&C أنظمة*\r\n\r\nتصميم مزرعة الخزانات ، بما في ذلك الضوابط وأنظمة المراقبة المتطورة*\r\n\r\nالتحكم المتقدم في وحدات المصفاة باستخدام خوارزميات التحكم في القيود التنبؤية متعددة المتغيرات*\r\n\r\nESD و F&G درجة SIL 3 أنظمة*\r\n\r\nمرافق تخزين الغاز ، وضغط الغاز المنبعث*\r\n\r\nمحطات نقل وتوزيع الغاز الطبيعي*\r\n\r\n  الأمن الإلكتروني*\r\n\r\nأنظمة مكافحة التسلل والكشف عن الحرارة*', NULL, 'النفط-والغاز-الطبيعي', '[]', '2020-05-03 17:12:19', '2020-11-09 15:36:15', 'ar'),
(41, 8, 'Petrol ve Doğalgaz', 'Kontrolmatik çözüm ortakları ile petrol rafinerileri ve petrol endüstrisinde tüm elektrifikasyon, enstrümantasyon ve otomasyon çözümlerini sunmakta ve rafinerilerde farklı işletme birimlerinde deneyimlerini paylaşmaktadır.\r\n\r\n* Atmosferik / Vakumlu Ham Üniteler\r\n* Visbreaker\r\n* Reformlama (Konvansiyonel ve CCR)\r\n* Hidrodesülfürizasyon\r\n* FCCU Sıvı Katalitik Kırma Ünitesi\r\n* Kükürt Geri Kazanımı ve TGT (Tail Gas Treating) Baca Gazı Arıtma\r\n* Alkilasyon\r\n* İzomerleştirme\r\n* Dimersol Ünitesi\r\n* Tank Sahası ve Karıştırma\r\n* LPG Depolama Boşaltma / Yükleme İstasyonları\r\n* Gaz Flare Ünitesi\r\n* Besleme ve Altyapı Sistemleri \r\n\r\nKontrolmatik farklı coğrafyalarda hem yeni hem de retrofit projeler için elektrifikasyon, enstrümantasyon ve kontrol sistemleri için özel çözümler, hizmetler ve ürünler sunmaktadır. \r\n\r\n* Anahtar Teslim 0larak E-I&C (Elektrik-Enstrüman-Kontrol) Sistemleri\r\n* Gelişmiş Kontroller Ve İzleme Sistemleri Dahil Olmak Üzere Tank Sahası Tasarımı\r\n* Çok Değişkenli Kestirim Kısıtlama Kontrol Algoritmaları Kullanılarak Rafineri Birimlerinin Gelişmiş Kontrolü\r\n* SIL 3 Derece F&G (Yangın ve Gaz Kontrol) ve ESD (Acil Durdurma) Sistemleri\r\n* Gaz Depolama Tesisleri, Gaz Dışı Sıkıştırma\r\n* Doğal Gaz Boru Hattı Taşıma Ve Dağıtım İstasyonları\r\n* Siber Güvenlik\r\n* İzinsiz Giriş Ve Isı Algılama Sistemleri', NULL, 'petrol-ve-dogalgaz', '[{\"download_link\":\"sector\\/May2020\\/UZt65Z5imMoONoadQuhr.png\",\"original_name\":\"logo-sv.png\"}]', '2020-05-03 17:12:47', '2021-02-24 16:02:00', 'tr'),
(42, 9, 'Transportation Sector l Kontrolmatik', '**Kontrolmatik provides wide range of services for Transportation:**\r\n* Subways\r\n* LRTs\r\n* Railways\r\n* Road Tunnels\r\n* Bridge\r\n* Airports\r\n* Shipping Ports\r\n* Train Stations\r\n\r\n**Highways**\r\n* Tunnel Control and SCADA centers\r\n* Traffic Control and Management Systems\r\n* Tunnel JetFan Systems\r\n* Tunnel Lighting Fixtures and Control Systems\r\n* MV&LV Distribution Switchgears\r\n* Emergency Power Supply Systems\r\n* Fire Detection and Fighting Systems\r\n* IP Camera and CCTV Systems\r\n* Traffic Signalization Systems\r\n* Vehicle Tracking and Classification Systems\r\n* Computational Fluid Dynamics Systems ( CFD)\r\n* Driver Information Systems\r\n* Communication Infrastructure Systems\r\n\r\n**Railways**\r\n* Total Solution for Electric Systems\r\n* Distributed RTU structures and control systems\r\n* Power Factor Correction and Quality solutions\r\n* Static VAr Compensation Units SVC/SVG/STAATCOM\r\n* SCADA and power control centers\r\n* ICCP Tele-control and Telecommand Centers\r\n\r\n**Metro and Light-Railways Systems**\r\n* SIMS and ECS (Environmental Control System) and mechanical equipment\r\n* SCADA Systems and related panels\r\n* In-house design and manufacturing for MDP LDP/MCCs\r\n* Computational Fluid Dynamics Systems ( CFD)\r\n* Tunnel Ventilation and Smoke Extraction Systems\r\n* IHK operation scenarios and test procedures\r\n* Tunnel Fire Fighting scenarios and test procedures\r\n* Tunnel Ventilation System Panels and its control systems\r\n* Tunnel JetFan Systems\r\n* Elevators and Escalators\r\n* Automatic Gate controllers\r\n\r\n***APPLICATIONS IN TRANSPORTATION SYSTEMS***\r\n\r\n**Lighting Control**\r\nTunnel entrance, interior and emergency lighting levels are adjusted according to the outdoor light level.\r\n\r\n**JetFan Control**\r\nVentilation is provided by jet-fans which are\r\nactivated in case of smoke formation and prevent to\r\npossible accumulation of exhaust gases in the\r\ntunnel. Jet fans also plays an active role in smoke\r\nevacuation in case of fire inside the tunnel.\r\nTraffic Signalization Systems\r\nThe system is control and coordinate to traffic lights,\r\nvariable speed signals, lane control signals, fog\r\nlamps, variable message signals (VMS / VTS)\r\nin the tunnel and tunnel en trance.\r\nCCTV and Event Detection System\r\nThe status of the tunnels is examined physically\r\nthrough cameras placed in the tunnel en trance,\r\ninterior sections and exits. The system continuously\r\ntracks the vehicle classifications, accidents, standing\r\nvehicles, reverse vehicles detection, pedestrian\r\ndetection outside the vehicle and vehicle navigation\r\nspeeds.\r\n\r\n**Passenger Information Systems**\r\nPassengers are informed about location of the\r\nupcoming vehicle, possible changes for the\r\nexpedition time and the estimated time of\r\narrival vehicle.\r\n\r\n**MV&LV Switchgears and Substation Automation**\r\nMonitoring and controlling of the systems such as\r\ntransformers, diesel generators, LV and MV\r\nswitchgears and uninterruptible power supply\r\nsystems are carried out in order to ensure\r\ncontinuous operation of the entire facility.\r\n\r\n**CFD Analysis**\r\nThat is the analysis for the evacuation of exhaust\r\ngases that can accumulate in the tunnel, smoke\r\nemission and calculation of temperature distributions\r\nin the case of fire and determination of whether the\r\nemergency fans will function as programmed and\r\ncalculation of actual fan forces and their position\r\nchanges if necessary.\r\nFire Fighting and Security Systems\r\nThe fire inside the tunnel is detected as soon as\r\npossible and extinguished in the shortest time frame\r\nand thus ensure the continuity of tunnel security.\r\n\r\n**ECS**\r\nECS is a common platform for the different\r\nmonitoring and control systems such as HVAC,\r\nplumbing and drainage systems, day/nighttime and\r\nemergency lighting systems, fire detection and alarm\r\nsystems, emergency announcement and evacuation\r\nguidance systems, turnstiles, access control and\r\nescalators/elevators. The escalators/elevators,\r\nturnstiles and access control systems are serving as\r\npackage type control systems with passenger\r\ninformation interfaces that provides data transfers\r\nvia standard communication protocols.\r\n\r\n**MCC Switchgear Manufacturing**\r\nMotor Control Centers are an integral part of the LV\r\nsystem as well as an important part of the control\r\nsystems. In all installed MCC systems used standard\r\ndistribution boards (including Form 4b) have been\r\nmanufacturing according to IEC 60439-1.\r\n\r\n**Telecomand and Control Room Solutions**\r\nKontrolmatik provides all the solutions you need with its expert staff in control and management centers.\r\n\r\nVideowall Systems (DLP cube)\r\nDLP cube solutions are more professional imaging\r\nsystems than LCD / Plasma equipment and display\r\ncubes can be arranged according to the needs/\r\ndimensions of the control center. Because of the\r\nscreens are not framed, there will be no loss o f image\r\nquality and they can operate 24/7.\r\n\r\nDLP Cube application locations\r\n* Control and Monitoring Rooms\r\n* Disaster and city coordination centers\r\n* Metro and railway signaling center\r\n* Telecommand Headquarters\r\n* SCADA Control Centers\r\n\r\nAdvantages of the DLP Cube system\r\n* Very Large Screen\r\n* High resolution\r\n* Working zones for multiple groups\r\n* User friendly, ease of use\r\n* Eliminating data loss\r\n* Redundant system\r\n\r\n[Transportation Brochure](https://www.kontrolmatik.com/main-laravel/laravel/storage/app/public/brochures/April2020/XbiW3eJKgv2ml8QnEzYL.pdf)', NULL, 'transportation', '[{\"download_link\":\"sector\\/May2020\\/srRRbwI7dJbXrVhS7soO.pdf\",\"original_name\":\"transportation.pdf\"}]', '2020-05-03 17:13:58', '2020-05-07 09:45:55', 'en');
