\n<p><img style=\"width: 500px; height: 374.101px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"media/1096/about159cb.png?width=500&amp;height=374.1007194244604\" alt=\"\" data-udi=\"umb://media/de1432e87cc04d0982a25ea5531a882e\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"parallax-about\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n<h3>SYSTEM INTEGRATOR GIANTS 2018 LIST</h3>\n<p>Kontrolmatik has been named the 52nd largest System Integrator in the world by Control Engineering, according to their just-released System Integrator Giants 2018 list.</p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 280px; height: 160px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"media/1010/si-giants-20186189.png?width=280&amp;height=160\" alt=\"\" data-udi=\"umb://media/319d43ab40d7436ba8b9842e72784610\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- homefooter form -->\n<div class=\"homefooter-form\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\n<h3>CONTACT</h3>\n<div class=\"text\">Want to know more? Contact us about product information and pricing, customer feedback, stockholder services, or just to voice a concern.</div>\n<div class=\"btn btn-black\">GET STARTED</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8 col-xs-12 mnopadding\">\n<h3>Get in Touch</h3>\n<form id=\"appointment-form\" action=\"http://form.hoopsdigital.com/NoDelete/Mail/Kontrolmatik/Mail.php\" method=\"post\" name=\"appointment-form\">\n<div class=\"col-md-12 clearfix mnopadding\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-xs-12 mnopadding\">\n<div class=\"form-group\"><input id=\"form_name\" name=\"form_name\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Your name\" /></div>\n<div class=\"form-group\"><input id=\"form_email\" name=\"form_email\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"E-Mail Address\" /></div>\n<div class=\"form-group\"><input id=\"form_phone\" name=\"form_phone\" type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Phone No\" /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6 col-xs-12 mnopadding\">\n<div class=\"form-group\"><textarea id=\"form_message\" class=\"form-control\" name=\"form_message\" required=\"\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\"></textarea></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-12\"><button class=\"btn btn-red\" type=\"submit\">Send Message</button></div>\n</form></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- homefooter form end --><footer>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"col-md-1 footerlogo\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"images/logoIcon.png\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-3 col-xs-12 social\">\n<ul class=\"social-network social-circle\">\n<li>&nbsp;</li>\n<li>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</footer>\n<div class=\"col-md-12 footerinfo\">&copy; 2018 - All rights reserved</div>\n<!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap\'s JavaScript plugins) -->\n<p></p>\n<!--<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js\"></script>-->\n<p></p>\n<!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed --><!-- Mirrored from www.kontrolmatik.com/about-us by HTTrack Website Copier/3.x [XR&CO\'2005], Tue, 09 Jul 2019 07:38:21 GMT -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- Added by HTTrack --><!-- /Added by HTTrack -->', '2019-08-02 07:13:58', '2019-08-02 07:13:58'),
