(946, 'pages', 'body', 25, 'fr', '**Quality Policy**\r\n\r\nKontrolmatik **commits;**\r\n\r\nDocumenting, certifying and continuously improving our quality management system to meet the requirements of **ISO 9001: 2015** standard,\r\nBased on the Total Quality philosophy, achieving the company and unit targets within the team spirit,\r\nReviewing business processes through self-evaluation process, identifying preventive approaches to improve performance,\r\nIncreasing the efficiency of all processes to internationally competitive level in line with the continuous improvement approach,\r\nEncouraging innovative and creative approaches, managing the activities to increase technical and behavioral competencies in an integrated way with Environmental, Occupational Health and Safety Management Systems.\r\n\r\n**Environment Policy**\r\n\r\nKontrolmatik **commits;**\r\n\r\n* To protect our environment and to ensure continuity, by observing all environmental laws and regulations to control the environmental impacts and reducing the impact of our environmental performance by continuously improving and realizing this awareness, to leave a clean environmentable environment for future generations.\r\n* To provide continuous improvement and improvement by providing all legal requirements and environmental requirements.\r\n* To consider environmental impacts in production investments.\r\n* Minimizing all our wastes, preventing pollution at the source, reclaiming as much as possible, eliminating the non-recyclable wastes in a way that will not harm the environment, thus reducing the effects on the environment.\r\n* To educate our employees, suppliers and subcontractors about the environment by raising environmental awareness.\r\n* To continuously improve our environmental management system in order to increase our environmental performance.\r\n* To undertake periodic reviews to achieve these goals and objectives.', '2019-09-04 07:27:26', '2019-09-04 07:27:26'),
