(4565, 'pages', 'body', 4, 'tr', 'Safety is more than a policy manual or a training video; it’s how we do business and it’s how we live 24/7. Kontrolmatik invites you to experience our culture of caring – a culture in which safety, health and welfare are top priorities; and in which we’re all responsible for looking out for one another.\n\nKontrolmatik\'s safety culture extends outside the office walls, beyond the project site and into our cars, our homes, and our communities; affecting all the people we interact with everywhere around the world. It’s about every one of us making safety a personal value that we live by each day.', '2020-04-27 07:40:51', '2020-04-27 07:40:51'),
