(4577, 'pages', 'body', 5, 'tr', 'Innovation is a driving force in our business, the need to improve spans people, processes and technology and we are always looking for better ways to deliver for the benefit of our customers and our business.\n\nAt Kontrolmatik we bring new thinking and fresh ideas to every project. Our drive to continuously improve runs throughout our organisation.\n\nA key part of our culture, innovation applies to our people, processes and technologies; pushing us to perform better and constantly look for opportunities to move our business forward.\n\nOur ever growing range of services brings new and exciting connections to technologies and methods that lead the way across our business. We draw from wider industry best practice in dozens of markets across hundreds of locations to offer fresh approaches and new solutions.', '2020-04-27 08:04:35', '2020-04-27 08:04:35'),
