(5391, 'posts', 'body', 324, 'tr', 'Voltage Level: 110 kV Substation and High Voltage Transmission Line\r\n\r\n**PROJECT SCOPE **\r\n\r\n* Design and Supply of 110 kV Substation Primary and Secondary Systems\r\n* Design of 110 kV Transmission Line\r\n* Supply of Some Components for 110 kV Transmission Line\r\n\r\n**DETAILED SCOPE OF SUPPLY**\r\n\r\n* Design and engineering works for substation\r\n* Design and engineering works for transmission Line \r\n* Voltage transformer 123 kV \r\n		o	Simultaneous Burden – 150 VA\r\nDisconnector with earthing switch 123kV , 1250 A , 31,5kA/3sec , enter Break type, 3-pole common DC motor\r\n		o	Motor supply Voltage - 110 V DC, Control Voltage = 110V DC and 230VAC \r\n* Current Transformer 123 kV ,31,5 kA /3sec , 31 mm/kV\r\n* Circuit Breaker 123 kV, 1250A, Single Pole operated 31,5 kA /3 sec, equipped with 110 V DC operated spring charged motor\r\n		o	Control Voltage = 110V DC and 220VAC for auxiliary requirement having phase-to-phase distance min 1,7 m, and Creepage Distance =31 mm/kV \r\n* Disconnector 123kV , 1250 A , 31,5kA/3sec ,Creepage Distance =31 mm/kV ,Center Break type, 3-pole common DC motor/ manual operated main blades\r\n* Motor supply Voltage - 110 V DC, Control Voltage = 110V DC and 230VAC \r\n* Surge arrestor Highest system Voltage = 123 kV\r\n		o	Rated Voltage Ur= 96 kV , 10 kA \r\n* Post Insulators required for the connection to Busbars\r\n* Aluminium conductor and Connections \r\n* Tension and suspension sets and insulators all hardwares with chain insulators, OPGW junction Bbox for extended part\r\n* Steel structure equipment supports, anchor bolts and templates for extended part\r\n* Earthing conductor and accessories, galvanized flat steel conductor for overground earthing of equipment and its supports with all required clamps and connectors\r\n* Cable supports, all cable supporting systems within 110 kV line feeder extension area\r\n* Low voltage and control cables PVC insulated without armor control & LV power cables of 110 kV Line Feeder extension area including termination & accessories\r\n* Relay protection panel 110kV\r\n* Busbar protection panel integration to existing BBP system\r\n* Control panel 110kV \r\n* Marshalling Kiosk 110 kV \r\n* RTU/SCADA SYSTEM Integration of 110 kV Line Bay to Existing RTU/ SCADA System of Nejrab Substation', '2020-05-07 16:38:42', '2020-05-07 16:38:42'),
